README for Curses::Menu

About:

  Curses::Menu is a Perl5 module for providing a simple menu interface
  to users using the Curses interface to perform text
  positioning/layout.

  Copyright (C) 2005, Chris Collins.  All rights reserved.

  This module is released under the modified BSD license.  Please see
  Copying.

Preqequisites:

  * Curses

How to install:

  In your favourite shell:

  $ perl Makefile.PL
  $ make
  $ make install

  (No test-suite yet).

Changes:

  1.00 :

    * First release

Planned Enhancements:

  * None yet.

